overrideProperties.name: Frogman Scrim Net (Black)
overrideProperties.description: Frogman camo veil is premium quality army scrim net scarf, a really useful large size, unlike other scrim scarves that are barely long enough to fit round your neck.Scarf measures 120cm x 150 cm with a stitched hem on two sides, manufactured from 100% cotton. Excellent as a sniper veil, helmet netting, head wrap or simply as a scarf. Ideal for all outdoor activities. Scrim scarves are designed to retain heat in cold conditions and helps keep you cool in hot conditions.
